includes Christopher Walken and Blair Brown. Belasco. Telecharge. Closes March
11.
</P>
<P>
	   --"The Lion King," director Julie Taymor's stage musical version of the
Disney cartoon hit. New Amsterdam. Ticketmaster. Difficult.
</P>
