<HEADLINE> Monaco's Prince Ranier Recovering  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   MONTE CARLO, Monaco (AP) -- Prince Rainier of Monaco is recovering well after
an operation to remove part of his lung.
</P>
<P>
	   The palace issued a statement Thursday saying ``the evolution of (Rainier's)
health is very favorable.''
</P>
<P>
	   Doctors at the Heart and Lung Center in Monaco successfully removed part of
Rainier's lung Wednesday. It was the second time in less than two months that
