with bonus payments for efficiency steps. They claimed the steps came at their
expense. Oxenberge aid 50 workers have been fired so far.
</P>
<P>
	   The Airport Authority responded that a new labor agreement has been
negotiated, but the union refuses to sign it.
</P>
